"amend" pairid="429" groupid="319" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">for a vehicle registered in this state, issue notice to the registered owner by mail or <ln numlevel="1" lineno="99" slineno="1-75"/>by personal service within 30 days after the day of the alleged violation; or</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-169" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="100" slineno="1-76" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3" tab="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1042" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="464" groupid="346" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">for a vehicle registered in another state, issue notice to the registered owner by <ln numlevel="1" lineno="101" slineno="1-77"/>mail or personal service within 60 days after the date of the alleged violation.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-170" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="102" slineno="1-78" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1043" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="479" groupid="357" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">A notice issued by an applicable law enforcement agency as described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="41-6a-312(8)(a)"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="103" slineno="1-79"/>(8)(a)</xref> shall:</amend><subsection ssid="1-null-171" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="104" slineno="1-80" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1044" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="486" groupid="363" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">provide information and evidence of the alleged violation, including the <ln n